attributes.review: This is the most terrible app I think I’ve ever downloaded. The orange monster’s face is the first thing you have to see when you open the app. 🤢 Even worse, he’s holding up the world’s tiniest fist like a little baby that’s banging on a table because he’s not getting enough attention. Seeing this made my stomach hurt, I actually thought I might puke. Luckily, I closed out of the app fast enough and thinking about Obama’s sweet handsome face calmed me down. Deleting this off my phone immediately. I hope Apple will do us all a favor and delete this from the App Store asap so we can save other innocent people from enduring the trauma that is experienced from downloading and opening this app.
attributes.title: WORST APP EVER
